Depends: R(>= 4.4), methods, RGraphSpace(>= 1.1.0), PathwaySpace(>= 1.0.3)
Imports: igraph, RANN
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, testthat, Seurat, SeuratObject, SeuratData, patchwork
Description: The SpotSpace package extends PathwaySpace to support analysis of spatial transcriptomics data. It provides methods for integrating spot-level coordinates with network-based projections, allowing spatial mapping, nearest-neighbor searches, and signal propagation in tissue sections.
